                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>Since Benghazi had been designated co-capital of Libya in December 1953, the
                    Consulate in Benghazi was designated a Legation, along with the Legation in
                    Tripoli, in February 1954.</p>
            </div>
